            <div>
                <h2>Bones</h2>
                <h4>43 Rue Godefroy Cavaignac, 75011 Paris</h4>
                <p>I had an awesome meal here. The homemade charcuterie is wow! And their sommelier is incredible. The day after I ate here, we all went to a wine tasting at Le Dauphin. Bone’s sommelier danced on the bar and broke his arm ! Nonetheless, in the chaos I mentioned that I would like to cook with James Henry and he texts him straight away to set up a 4 hands dinner.  That’s commitment!</p>
                {{#if session.user}}
