            </div>
            <div>
                <h2>Epicure, Le Bristol</h2>
                <h4>112 Rue du Faubourg Saint-Honoré, 75008 Paris</h4>
                <p>Surely I can dress up IF it’s for a good cause! Excellent French food here, of course.</p>
                {{#if session.user}}
